translations: v．精心打扮，讲究穿着：指花时间和精力使自己看起来整洁、时尚。
· She primped herself in front of the mirror before going out.
她在出门前在镜子前精心打扮了一番。

sentences.sentence: Getting ready for work in the morning, looking primped and polished, can be a major time suck.
sentences.translation: 每天早上要为上班做好准备，让自己看起来光鲜亮丽，这个过程可能会很耗时。
